  27,74,Tuus Dominus fully knows quod their chests hide quod they declare
  27,75,(ibi est nihil caelum terra hidden Deus;) everything est profound actum
  27,76,Hoc Quran settles multus proles Infans Israel; proles ut they adhuc disputing
  27,77,multus assuredly it est guide mercy believers
